org.cef.handler

Class CefDisplayHandlerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.handler.CefDisplayHandlerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CefDisplayHandler

    public abstract class CefDisplayHandlerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements CefDisplayHandler
    An abstract adapter class for receiving display events. The methods in this class are empty. This class exists as convenience for creating handler objects.
